timeline.bodyText: I'm sorry about all of these. Intellij feels the there shouldn't be a trailing space, and our style guide has no rule for this. I think Eclipse uses trailing spaces for javadocs.
timeline.author: hmottestad

replies.bodyText: Fwiw I agree with IntelliJ here. I'll take a look at my eclipse settings to see if I can get it to remove these trailing whitespaces.
